英國經濟會有實質益處</span></ins></strong>&rdquo; (p. 8). 最後, <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">英國幫BNO升級可顯示英國&rdquo;並未忘記其角色和放棄原則&rdquo;</span></ins></strong> (p. 9). 這份報告暗示: a. BNO是&rdquo;和平時代&rdquo;的產物. 只要中英間利益衝突, BNO會是英國的招數: 中國領土內突然出現大批BC會<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">使英國有理由介入香港事務</span></ins></strong>, 這也是為什麼當初英國不給港人BC身份, 卻要弄出BNO, 而中國則要強加中國籍給香港人的根本原因 (英國不要收留港人; 中國收港人, 但條件是&rdquo;管得了&rdquo;的港人. 反正要抓人只要說句他是&rdquo;中國人&rdquo;就行) (結論1和3); b. 英國對香港的&rdquo;道義和責任&rdquo;乃建基在利益上, 尤其<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">正值英國脫歐, 香港將可成為英國經濟的救火員</span></ins></strong> (結論2)."},{"pid":"06359c669b00c31b3bce3d062bbfc18022f6ec4a","tid":1508177,"uid":97258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:25:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"740e3d32f0d88648942e6b275dc749251912650b","tid":1508177,"uid":16458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf1676df332bac85456f2b35a978624b9b60c51","tid":1508177,"uid":143183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:41:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a4a81b3343704f4e6bc94693ed9f402408f64aa3","tid":1508177,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860370c5291db1bc23d5b4da7f435266366b1229","tid":1508177,"uid":550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:53:01.000Z","msg":"好似有人講過 香港關係法承認BNO=特衰<br />\n如果BNO免簽 首先要取消/修改關係法先<br />\n加上夏千福講過VWP只限主權國家<br />\n以前老曾遊說過特衰免簽都失敗<br />\n除非香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e15fa5d03ba3adcd7866917c84ef2f21669107","tid":1508177,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"860370c5291db1